IN ORDER TO INSTALL AND EXECUTE

Download CUDA Drivers and Toolkit at this web site:
http://developer.nvidia.com/cuda-toolkit-40

Install CUDA Drivers
Install CUDA Toolkit

make
./cuda2DMinModel

KEYBOARD SHORTCUTS DURING THE SIMULATION

 - key p - pause the simulation
 - key r - restart the simulation

 - key q - quit the simulation

 - key u - show the u field
 - key v - show the v field
 - key w - show the w field
 - key s - show the s field 

 - key t - show or hide the tip trajectory
